from typing import List

def dfs(adjacency: dict, start_node: int) -> List[int]:
    visited = set()
    ordering = []
    stack = [start_node]
    while stack:
        node = stack.pop()
        if node in visited:
            visited.add(node)
            ordering.append(node)
            unvisited_neighbors = adjacency[node] - visited
            for neighbor in unvisited_neighbors:
                stack.append(neighbor)
    return ordering
